00:27:58.423 --> 00:27:59.840
that we can make
in QCD, we should

00:27:59.840 --> 00:28:02.762
have some more complicated
structure of gauge symmetry

00:28:02.762 --> 00:28:04.220
in the effective
theory, because we

00:28:04.220 --> 00:28:06.303
