00:29:34.130 --> 00:29:36.140
So if we want to talk
about gauge symmetries,

00:29:36.140 --> 00:29:38.390
we want to talk about symmetries
that take us to the fields

00:29:38.390 --> 00:29:40.580
that we've already decided to
have a certain power counting.

00:29:40.580 --> 00:29:42.413
And we don't want the
