00:31:30.200 --> 00:31:40.040
in momentum space, and that's
because gauge transformations

00:31:40.040 --> 00:31:41.870
are local transformations.

00:31:41.870 --> 00:31:46.160
Local means local
in x not in P. So

00:31:46.160 --> 00:31:48.890
