01:00:24.920 --> 01:00:32.350
So let's think
about, so I told you

01:00:32.350 --> 01:00:35.200
how this Wilson line
transforms under Uc see.

01:00:35.200 --> 01:00:40.120
How does it transform
under U ultrasoft?

01:00:40.120 --> 01:00:49.410
So under Uc, again using
this matrix-type notation,

01:00:49.410 --> 01:00:50.635
it's just Uc.

01:00:57.110 --> 01:00:58.610
So this is a matrix
multiplication

01:00:58.610 --> 01:00:59.600
in momentum space.

01:01:07.850 --> 01:01:12.350
What about under an
ultrasoft transformation?

01:01:12.350 --> 01:01:14.390
Well, under an ultrasoft
transformation,

01:01:14.390 --> 01:01:15.850
this should be a derived--

01:01:15.850 --> 01:01:17.850
in some sense, under a
collinear transformation,

01:01:17.850 --> 01:01:19.600
it was a derived
quantity, because we knew

01:01:19.600 --> 01:01:20.948
of the gauge field transform.

01:01:20.948 --> 01:01:23.240
The thing that gave us the
transformation of the Wilson

01:01:23.240 --> 01:01:25.680
line is just the transformation
of the gauge field.

01:01:25.680 --> 01:01:26.180
OK?

01:01:26.180 --> 01:01:29.030
So that's what led to,
actually, this form, once we

01:01:29.030 --> 01:01:30.240
put in this fact.

01:01:30.240 --> 01:01:31.970
So under the ultrasoft
transformation,

01:01:31.970 --> 01:01:34.553
we just take the transformation
that we have for the collinear

01:01:34.553 --> 01:01:36.530
gauge field, and
then we derive how

01:01:36.530 --> 01:01:41.360
the Wilson line should transform
under the ultrasoft gauge

01:01:41.360 --> 01:01:42.510
symmetry.

01:01:42.510 --> 01:01:43.010
OK?

01:01:43.010 --> 01:01:45.800
So how does this guy transform?

01:01:45.800 --> 01:01:49.160
This guy transforms by
putting U's on the left

01:01:49.160 --> 01:01:57.190
and the right that are at x.

01:01:57.190 --> 01:01:58.840
But every field in
this exponential

01:01:58.840 --> 01:02:02.260
has the same, U U
dagger, multiply it,

01:02:02.260 --> 01:02:04.120
think about expanding that out.

01:02:04.120 --> 01:02:06.470
All the U U daggers that are
next to each other cancel.

01:02:06.470 --> 01:02:08.595
You just get an overall U
U dagger that comes right

01:02:08.595 --> 01:02:10.670
outside the exponential.

01:02:10.670 --> 01:02:16.960
So this guy is just transforming
with U ultrasoft of x.

01:02:16.960 --> 01:02:23.440
Wilson line back again,
U ultrasoft dagger of x,

01:02:23.440 --> 01:02:26.200
and that's because this
Wilson line with our notation

01:02:26.200 --> 01:02:29.470
is really a local thing with
respect to the coordinate x.

01:02:29.470 --> 01:02:31.640
All the fields sit at x.

01:02:31.640 --> 01:02:32.140
OK?

01:02:32.140 --> 01:02:35.500
So it just transforms
like that, because that's

01:02:35.500 --> 01:02:39.359
how the gauge field
inside it transforms.

01:02:48.840 --> 01:02:50.310
So in some sense,
both of these are

01:02:50.310 --> 01:02:52.030
derived from the
transformation of An,

01:02:52.030 --> 01:02:56.277
but it's easier to think about
how a Wilson line transforms

01:02:56.277 --> 01:02:58.110
and then think about
how it should transform

01:02:58.110 --> 01:03:00.410
under collinear than just
go through the An route

01:03:00.410 --> 01:03:03.070
and impose this condition.

01:03:03.070 --> 01:03:03.570
OK.

01:03:03.570 --> 01:03:10.020
So let's come back now to our
full current which was this,

01:03:10.020 --> 01:03:13.590
that had the Wilson line in it.

01:03:13.590 --> 01:03:16.410
And now if you ask how
it transforms under Uc,

01:03:16.410 --> 01:03:19.560
you see what's going to happen.

01:03:19.560 --> 01:03:24.720
You get Uc dagger, Uc,
and the ultrasoft guy

01:03:24.720 --> 01:03:27.720
doesn't transform,
and then these cancel.

01:03:27.720 --> 01:03:31.050
So it's invariant under
the transformations

01:03:31.050 --> 01:03:33.380
that have momenta of
order of the ultrasoft.

01:03:33.380 --> 01:03:35.610
It'll have a momentum of
what are the linear scale.

01:03:35.610 --> 01:03:38.070
There's two objects in this
thing that have momenta

01:03:38.070 --> 01:03:39.210
that can be of that size.

01:03:39.210 --> 01:03:42.180
The gluons, they're in W in
