So this current that
we derived earlier

01:04:37.990 --> 01:04:40.690
is actually invariant under two
different types of symmetries

01:04:40.690 --> 01:04:44.230
which are really momentum space
splitting of a standard gauge

01:04:44.230 --> 01:04:47.380
symmetry into pieces where we
have a large momenta and pieces

01:04:47.380 --> 01:04:49.390
where you have these
larger momenta, collinear

01:04:49.390 --> 01:04:51.370
momenta and pieces where
we have a smaller momenta,

01:04:51.370 --> 01:04:52.360
this ultrasoft momenta.

01:04:52.360 --> 01:04:53.777
But both of these
types of momenta

01:04:53.777 --> 01:04:57.790
are momenta that we're allowing
inside the effective theory.

01:04:57.790 --> 01:04:58.440
Yeah?

01:04:58.440 --> 01:04:59.815
AUDIENCE: Just
